WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.990 align:middle line:90%


00:00:00.990 --> 00:00:04.620 align:middle line:84%
>> Scientists announce they
have finally completed the map

00:00:04.620 --> 00:00:07.020 align:middle line:90%
of the entire human genome.

00:00:07.020 --> 00:00:09.990 align:middle line:84%
Will the information
contained within unlock

00:00:09.990 --> 00:00:12.870 align:middle line:84%
our true potential for
health and well-being,

00:00:12.870 --> 00:00:16.650 align:middle line:84%
or is there another, more
expansive perspective

00:00:16.650 --> 00:00:19.840 align:middle line:84%
on the role genes
play in our lives?

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:22.650 align:middle line:84%
>> It's not the
genes that count now.

00:00:22.650 --> 00:00:26.070 align:middle line:84%
It's how we respond
to the environment,

00:00:26.070 --> 00:00:30.940 align:middle line:84%
how we respond to the signals
that we send to the genes.

00:00:30.940 --> 00:00:33.364 align:middle line:90%
>> This is Gaia News.

00:00:33.364 --> 00:00:36.752 align:middle line:90%
